                    <p>Big open exploration space: A focus on the visualization that gives the user the breathing room to full capture every detail they need.
                    </p>
                    <p>Key Requirements:</p>
                    <ul style="margin-top: 1rem;">
                        <li>Text match filters </li>
                        <li>Numeric members and range filters </li>
                        <li>Date range filters on time dimensions (including multiple date range filters)</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
